{"tid":1084921,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"武磊最大的短板是什么？他跟巅峰时期的郝海东能比吗？","createTime":"2019-03-30T18:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T18:30:44.000Z","uid":1426,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d8a622dfc74b0a4a61dd44d6e49100c95f6530ed","tid":1084921,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T18:14:29.000Z","msg":"客观的说<br />\n武磊已经体现了一点价值，今晚和加西亚的配合确实给巴萨带来了一点威胁<br />\n有点可惜放人太晚，武磊要是提前几年刘洋没准会有更亮眼的表现<br />\n不过武球王应该坐稳了主力了<br />\n<br />\n力度，硬度。力度不够，所以武球王几乎没有劲射、远射、暴射；硬度不够，所以武球王也不可能有孙球王的中场带球一条龙。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYorDJW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYorDJW.png&h=7a12e878&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8J0tR3X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8J0tR3X.png&h=413244ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59033b53ab24027119621a6d47a76db3aacaed39","tid":1084921,"uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T18:21:23.000Z","msg":"为啥没人回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab6bf1e8360e693b5d5813ab41465ce569fe519","tid":1084921,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T18:24:00.000Z","msg":"你今晚發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc454c3ed8603f88fc4224316b792d678fff8e8","tid":1084921,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T18:24:21.000Z","msg":"好尷尬"},{"pid":"c2090ed1513f0f67f46b710041e8f9ec66e317b7","tid":1084921,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9ab6bf1e8360e693b5d5813ab41465ce569fe519","tid":1084921,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T18:24:00.000Z","msg":"你今晚發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T18:27:15.000Z","msg":"希望㕷们一起支持杜马女士<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SDcW09G.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\